<object id="GUID-357D742B-C622-4D1E-88C8-A6786FD0DFB2" class="- topic/object "><desc class="- topic/desc "><p class="- topic/p ">Mark printhead(s) as empty </p></desc><param name="testid" value="046020" class="- topic/param "/><param name="target" value="NIL" class="- topic/param "/><param name="axmodule" value="None" class="- topic/param "/></object> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p ">Mark a printhead as empty. 
</p><note id="GUID-5EC6AD8F-EB49-4E8D-91CD-626CC2522B12" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">You must be in zero or cold SDS. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-92369981-F020-4E62-9707-58F93D054214" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Description</title><p class="- topic/p ">This will mark a printheads empty even when ink is detected by the level sensor. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> This will prevent ink dosing timeout errors. For instance when the boiler unit of a printhead is replaced. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the wrong printhead is disabled, select it again. (the value will toggle) 
</p></section><section id="GUID-BC805AF5-38C3-4741-9E22-AB35AED4B8D1" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Start the test. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the printhead to mark empty. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The value of the printhead will change to "Marked as empty" 
</p></li></ol></section><section id="GUID-A24D31FC-B964-4EA1-B0B1-1045C3A19EEF" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Values</title><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Marked as empty 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Not marked as empty 
</p></li></ul></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-686678F1-A321-4B08-84D3-63C9CD28C7FA.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>SDS</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
